                            <comment id="15352805" author="erans" created="Tue, 28 Jun 2016 11:18:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Could you make this patch against the development version?&lt;br/&gt;
It is in branch &quot;develop&quot; of the git repository.&lt;br/&gt;
